column2: select p.objid, p.type, p.clean, p.ra, p.dec, p.dered_u, p.dered_g, p.dered_r, p.dered_i, p.dered_z, p.err_u, p.err_g, p.err_r, p.err_i, p.err_z, pz.z, pz.zerr, pz.kcorrU, pz.kcorrI, pz.kcorrR, pz.kcorrI, pz.kcorrZ, pz.absMagU, pz.absMagG, pz.absMagR, pz.absMagI, pz.absMagZ, m.* into mydb.VAC_clean_GRGs_Photo from photoobj p, photoz pz, mydb.VAC_clean_GRGs m where p.objid = pz.objid and abs (p.ra - m.ID_ra) < = # and abs (p.dec - m.ID_dec) < = #
